        <div><span class="tg-kicker tg-kicker--light">Unlimited or pay as you go</span><h2>Use every surface your way.</h2><p>Subscribe for unlimited chat, UI tools, and provider APIs, or start free and add API credits when you need them.</p></div>
        <div class="tg-cta-row"><a href="/subscribe" class="tg-btn tg-btn--primary tg-btn--xl">View unlimited plan</a><a href="/signup" class="tg-btn tg-btn--secondary tg-btn--xl">Start free</a></div>
